column2: select   id, run, rerun, camcol, field, petroMag_u as upmag, petroMagErr_u as upmag_err,   petroMag_g as gpmag, petroMagErr_g as gpmag_err, petroMag_r as rpmag,    petroMagErr_r as rpmag_err, petroMag_i as ipmag, petroMagErr_i as ipmag_err,   petroMag_z as zpmag, petroMagErr_z as zpmag_err,    extinction_u as ext_u, extinction_g as ext_g, extinction_r as ext_r,    extinction_i as ext_i, extinction_z as ext_z   from MyDB.temp as t    left join PhotoObjAll as p on p.objID=t.objid    order by id
